-- BP on track to intercept well by August 15: U.S.
-- 
-- Fri Aug 6, 2010 12:25pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2010/08/06/us-oil-spill-allen-idUSTRE6743UD20100806

 

 HOUSTON  (Reuters) - BP Plc engineers expect to drill into the bottom of the blown-out Macondo well by August 15 in a bid to seal it once and for all with cement, the top U.S. spill official said on Friday. 

 (Reporting by  Chris Baltimore )